name: VaccinesSnomedCtIpsFreeSet
title: Vaccines - SNOMED CT IPS Free Set
publisher: Health Level Seven International - Patient Care Work Group
description: This value set includes the codes from the SNOMED International Patient Set (IPS) subset of SNOMED CT (IPS Free Set) that are included in: all descendants of 71181003 \|Product containing vaccine (product)\|.
